    "name": "Party Madness",
    "steam_appid": 3150970,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150970/extras/614041c5c65be47ca490fa9e7ad8b5f1.poster.avif?t=1763399509\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150970/extras/614041c5c65be47ca490fa9e7ad8b5f1.webm?t=1763399509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150970/extras/614041c5c65be47ca490fa9e7ad8b5f1.mp4?t=1763399509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Party Madness（派对狂欢）是一款支持2-4人在线游玩的派对游戏。和你的朋友一起在疯狂的小游戏中展开对战，收集积分，争夺胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的小游戏！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Party Madness中的每个小游戏都是一场混乱又刺激的冒险！你可能上一秒还在海洋中逃离愤怒的章鱼，下一秒就要在激光密布的银行抢劫中奔跑，接着还要在沙漠中驾驶车辆，躲避从天而降的陨石。躲避、欢笑、抢钱，一个都不能少！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150970/extras/8424c76829b7ef422faca0f098f92e68.poster.avif?t=1763399509\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150970/extras/8424c76829b7ef422faca0f098f92e68.webm?t=1763399509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150970/extras/8424c76829b7ef422faca0f098f92e68.mp4?t=1763399509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每一局都是新的挑战！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和朋友展开激烈对战，每一场游戏都会带来不同的挑战。驾驶赛车、在船上战斗，或者运用各种策略，在不同的小游戏中脱颖而出，赢得第一！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150970/extras/07a4c844a66ecb890e7db004b575f2b1.poster.avif?t=1763399509\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150970/extras/07a4c844a66ecb890e7db004b575f2b1.webm?t=1763399509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150970/extras/07a4c844a66ecb890e7db004b575f2b1.mp4?t=1763399509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>服装与个性化！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有丰富多样的服装供你选择，比如海盗、宇航员、武士等多种主题。通过游戏解锁更多新装扮，在每场比赛中展示你的独特风格！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150970/extras/e06e0d43b9e7045bbdc88a22463b8956.poster.avif?t=1763399509\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150970/extras/e06e0d43b9e7045bbdc88a22463b8956.webm?t=1763399509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150970/extras/e06e0d43b9e7045bbdc88a22463b8956.mp4?t=1763399509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好加入这场疯狂又有趣的派对了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Party Madness（派对狂欢）为你带来不停歇的动作、笑声和意想不到的冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >疯狂正在等你加入！</p>",
